<li> My heart goes out to you.  Is there anything I can do to ease your burden?</li>
<li> Deepest condolences.  Don't hesitate to call upon me for anything you might need.</li>
<li> So sorry for your loss.  I'm here to help in any way I can – just let me know.</li>
<li> Sending love and strength your way.  I'm available to help with whatever you need.</li>
